                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2060-18390708 t18390708-2060-punishment-49"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Third Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
